## Color legend

| Color | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| üü¢ Green | Usage below 70% ‚Äî all good |
| üü° Yellow | Usage 70‚Äì90% ‚Äî getting full |
| üî¥ Red | Usage above 90% ‚Äî critical |
